title: Ep 1225 - 3 big fans of Taarak Mehta
shortDesc: 3 big fans of Taarak Mehta - Taarak Mehta comes across his 3 biggest fans and also clicks photographs with them...

title: Ep 1226 - Tapus master plan to bring Bappa in Gokuldham
shortDesc: Tapu's master plan to bring Bappa in Gokuldham - Tapu Sena reveals to all the members of Gokuldham society that there are no funds to celebrate Ganesh Utsav...

title: Ep 1227 - Lord Ganesha arrives in Gokuldham society
shortDesc: Lord Ganesha arrives in Gokuldham society - Tapu Sena and all the members of Gokuldham society welcome Lord Ganesha in a musical way...

title: Ep 1228 - Members stunned to see Tapu Senas decoration
shortDesc: Members stunned to see Tapu Sena's decoration - All the members of Gokuldham society are stunned to see Tapu Sena's Ganesh Utsav decoration...

title: Ep 1229 - Hen becomes a huge trouble for society members
shortDesc: Hen becomes a huge trouble for society members - Tapu Sena reveals the punishment to all the members of Gokuldham Society...

title: Ep 1230 - Kaun Banega Murga
shortDesc: Kaun Banega Murga - Tapu Sena introduces their new variety Programme Kaun Banega Murga...

title: Ep 1231 - Funny task for Popatlal
shortDesc: Funny task for Popatlal - All the members of Gokuldham Society are giving their best performances...

title: Ep 1232 - Taarak Mehta recites poetry on Gokuldham Society
shortDesc: Taarak Mehta recites poetry on Gokuldham Society - Taarak Mehta gets a task to recite poetry...

title: Ep. 1233 - Bagha Gets Called To The Stage - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Roshani calls Bagha to the stage and asks him to perform. He is given a task to mimic an actor. Nattu kaka tells him not to spoil Jetha's name. But Bagha performs really well and entertains everyone.

title: Ep. 1234 - Iyer's Romantic Act - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Iyer is called to the stage and asked to say I love you to Babita is different languages. Jetha tries to make him nervous but Iyer finishes his act in a romantic way.

title: Ep. 1235 - A Tough Challenge For Jetha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha and Daya are given a very tough challenge. The task is to not dance when the music starts. Daya finds it very tough and Iyer wants Jetha to lose the challenge.

title: Ep. 1236 - Bhide Gets Furious - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tappu Sena makes fun of Bhide and tells him that he has done something wrong. Bhide gets furious and questions them about it. Tappu Sena worries about the financial condition of the society.

title: Ep. 1237 - Popatlal's Dreams Are Crushed - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: A lady come to the society and Popatlal starts dreaming of making her his wife. He flirts with her a bit and later finds out that she is already married. She is searching for her husband who is missing.

title: Ep. 1238 - Daya Disturbs Jetha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya calls Jetha when he's at work and disturbs him. She calls to inform him that Popatlal has gone to a hotel in search of that lady and gets into trouble. Jetha feels bad for Popatlal.

title: Ep. 1239 - Popatlal's Hotel Drama - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Potpatlal rushes into the Hotel and blames the manager for his ruined marriage. But the Manager tries to give him discounts to calm him down. Potpatlal is very depressed.
